data.title: Neo Geo:Neo Geo CD Exclusive Games
data.meta_description: The following games are exclusive to the Neo Geo CD either as a whole, in the home market, or in the Neo Geo family.[1]
data.text:
The following games are exclusive to the Neo Geo CD either as a whole, in the home market, or in the Neo Geo family.[1]

Games Exclusive to the Neo Geo CD

Ironclad: Tesshō Rusha (Chōtetsu Burikingā, BRIKIN'GER)

Crossed Swords II

ZinTrick (Oshidashi Zintorikku)

ADK World

Neo Geo CD Special

The King of Fighters '96 Neo Collection

Games Not Available on AES

Puzzle Bobble

Janshin Densetsu: Quest of Jongmaster

Power Spikes II

Neo Drift Out: New Technology

Pleasure Goal: 5 on 5 Mini Soccer (Futsal: 5-on-5 Mini Soccer)

Games Not Available on MVS/AES

Samurai Shodown RPG (Shinsetsu Samurai Spirits: Bushidō Retsuden) - Also available on PlayStation and Saturn.

Idol-Mahjong Final Romance 2 (arcade game port)

Known Prototypes

Bang² Busters [Bang Bang Busters]

Treasure of the Caribbean [Caribe no Zaihō]
